{"id":275289,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-天津失地村民冒着严寒持续在国土局抗议/","date":"2013-01-19T11:01:07Z","modified":"2013-01-19T11:01:07Z","title":"维权网 | 天津失地村民冒着严寒持续在国土局抗议（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员侯原民报道）本网信息员得到天津维权人士提供的信息，元月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>号，天寒地冻，天津南开区卧福里村民继续到天津国土局举行抗议活动，这已经是第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">53</span><span>天连续抗议了。村民们抗议国土局非法将卧福里村民的宅基地卖给了“地王”。（此前曾在维权网做过报道）卧福里村民们在没有得到补偿款的情况下，自己赖以生存的房屋被政府野蛮强拆，并抓捕了几个维权的村民。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>如今，无家可归的村民只能到国土局抗议和到各级政府部门告状，但村民们无家可归的问题始终没人管。自知理亏的国土局每每见到村民们的到来，就及时将大门紧紧的锁上，不接待村民的上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1PNN4g3Ak7s/UPo4cCZO4sI/AAAAAAAAZZs/lewAwvNYLPI/s1600/53.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1PNN4g3Ak7s/UPo4cCZO4sI/AAAAAAAAZZs/lewAwvNYLPI/s320/53.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-OaPd_umoa-4/UPo4c8fw2RI/AAAAAAAAZZw/IKw0LfRkgSU/s1600/54.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-OaPd_umoa-4/UPo4c8fw2RI/AAAAAAAAZZw/IKw0LfRkgSU/s320/54.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[182